{"tid":750131,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【找數真漢子】伊巴上BBC回碧咸：會著英軍波衫同食炸魚薯條","createTime":"2018-07-20T15:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T02:22:31.000Z","uid":161311,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3a1536cb3d0c7a45a703b7f880a9ee8ba7ff78","tid":750131,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"英格蘭於世界盃8強對瑞典賽前，伊巴謙莫域曾在網上向舊隊友碧咸「挑機」對賭，結果伊巴落敗。這位效力洛杉磯銀河的瑞典球星雖賽後已願賭服輸，但周四在《BBC》公開重申，願意穿上英格蘭球衣來溫布萊觀看英軍比賽，以及吃英國傳統美食炸魚薯條。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴當時曾下賭注，如瑞典勝出，他在宜家購買的所有傢俬，都要由碧咸埋單；相反若英軍勝出，碧咸便要伊巴穿上英軍球衣來到溫布萊，觀賞球隊比賽，期間還要吃炸魚薯條。這場比賽結果由英格蘭勝出，碧咸賽後已即刻在網上出帖，還特意改圖令伊巴穿上英格蘭波衫，等待他「找數」，而伊巴及後也已在ig回應，但只是簡單表示自己會去溫布萊。<br />\n伊巴周四接受《BBC》電視台訪問，便首次對著鏡頭向碧咸開腔：「大衛，我們對賭，然而我輸了；我會來溫布萊看英格蘭比賽，當然還會穿上英格蘭球衣，以及吃炸魚薯條。」他及後再補充：「在瑞典落敗後，給我一點時間透氣和冷靜，但現在可以了，我很期待比賽。」<br />\n英格蘭下一場國際賽於9月上演，會在歐洲國家聯賽與西班牙於溫布萊對壘，未知伊巴是否會在這場比賽穿上英軍球衣，在觀眾席上為他們打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180720/58463886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180720%2F58463886&d=lNOFKpRqpTM1Ydg%2BMRg%2B6S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1b727143\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180720%2F58463886&h=f279657e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180720/58463886</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/232648_0f54b834659794c177475e64ae4a0875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F232648_0f54b834659794c177475e64ae4a0875.jpg&h=c3c08800&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f66cb50c87f1f125b490ffc6a2d390d26a64201","tid":750131,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a53b9bdf0f3a950697054fdc3451ac397f02d6a","tid":750131,"uid":55050,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75214f1c8fc21f9485030e1ffe46ed25d30dcba4","tid":750131,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:03:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾黎"},{"pid":"936a9b6a2681637dc9c9fa9457d907f00e3a953d","tid":750131,"uid":27575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:09:28.000Z","msg":"找數真漢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e10f9f1e7511799075f1e4eaadc6bb5868cb38","tid":750131,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T02:18:20.000Z","msg":"型"},{"pid":"1e8ff0d87411bdcfcea9bef9b5018e728f5a37a2","tid":750131,"uid":176472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a53b9bdf0f3a950697054fdc3451ac397f02d6a","tid":750131,"uid":55050,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gi